thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Jason Babila

author: Jason Babila
title: Jason Babila
text:
I have never used a storage of any company before, there are numerous storages in the vicinity and a couple of PS not far from each other, I decided to go with PS and I went online to reserve me a spot.
When I got to the facility, the manager explained what I needed to know and he was easy to consult with.
